2nd Samadhi at Abayagiri Aramic Complex
This Buddha Statue and the Bodhi-ghara (Bo tree Shrine ) belongs to the 
. This site is popularly known as the 2nd Samadhi Statue of
. Though the origin of this statue is unknown, from the style of execution it is thought that the Buddha is in the Vitharka Posture and belongs to the 6-8th centuries.
 
